data.description: OPEN HOUSE CANCELLED 12/10/2023 ALL BRICK, 4 BEDROOM, NEW ROOF!  Many areas just painted!  On top of four bedrooms this house offers a flex room near the front door that leads to a spacious living area with a fireplace!  The master bathroom was recently remodeled and features a tile shower.  Fenced back yard with a shed.  New storm shelter in the garage!  825 W Berkeley is a great opportunity waiting for you in south Springfield!
